### List conversations - should return 200 OK with paginated list of conversations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?page=0&size=5

### Sorted by createdAt desc - should return newest conversations first with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?page=0&size=5&sort=createdAt,desc

### Sorted by createdAt asc - should return oldest conversations first
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?sort=createdAt,asc&size=5

### DELETE - non-existent id should return 404 with error body
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

